text: Novoarslanbekovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Sayranovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 150 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 47 km from Tuymazy, 5 km from Sayranovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Novoarslanbekovo
